
Aim

To define the attributes (data members) and methods (member functions) for each identified class in the Predictive Stock Management System.

Class Definitions
1. User

Attributes:

userId : int

username : String

password : String

role : String

Methods:

login()

logout()

changePassword()

2. Admin (inherits User)

Attributes:

adminId : int

Methods:

addUser()

updateUser()

deleteUser()

manageSuppliers()

generateAdminReport()

3. StoreManager (inherits User)

Attributes:

managerId : int

Methods:

viewStockLevels()

viewPredictions()

placeRestockOrder()

4. InventoryStaff (inherits User)

Attributes:

staffId : int

Methods:

recordSalesData()

updateInventory()

5. Product

Attributes:

productId : int

productName : String

category : String

unitPrice : double

Methods:

addProduct()

updateProductDetails()

removeProduct()

6. Inventory

Attributes:

inventoryId : int

quantityAvailable : int

reorderLevel : int

Methods:

updateStock()

checkStockLevel()

generateReorderAlert()

7. SalesData

Attributes:

salesId : int

saleDate : Date

quantitySold : int

Methods:

addSalesRecord()

getSalesHistory()

8. PredictionModel

Attributes:

modelId : int

modelType : String

accuracy : double

Methods:

analyzeSalesData()

predictDemand()

updateModel()

9. Supplier

Attributes:

supplierId : int

supplierName : String

contactDetails : String

Methods:

addSupplier()

updateSupplierDetails()

supplyProduct()

10. RestockOrder

Attributes:

orderId : int

orderDate : Date

orderQuantity : int

orderStatus : String

Methods:

createOrder()

updateOrderStatus()

cancelOrder()

11. Report

Attributes:

reportId : int

reportType : String

generatedDate : Date

Methods:

generateReport()

exportReport()

viewReport()

Class Inheritance Overview

User

Admin

StoreManager

InventoryStaff

Result

Attributes and methods for all identified classes were clearly defined for the Predictive Stock Management System.

Conclusion

Defining attributes and methods helps in designing a precise and modular class diagram. The Predictive Stock Management System follows object-oriented principles with clear class responsibilities.
